reviewText: awesome 1 price collection of seasons 1-4  we loved it, and so did my in-laws!
So funny and so entertaining. Must Buy

Very happy with this purchase.  My mother loves "Duck Dynasty" so this was the perfect gift for her.  The only drawback was that we couldn't find any subtitles, which was mainly a bother because of my grandmother and hearing-impaired aunt.  Perhaps they were there and we were too inept to find them.  In any case, this was well worth it.
this series is always wonderful cant wait to get season 5 when its released i could watch it over and over
